            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Licinus Phi<lb break="no" n="2"/>letus et Lici<lb break="no" n="3"/>nia Crassi <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erta</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Peregrina Isidi <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>loc</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ac</abbr><ex>cepto</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex cert="low">ublice</ex></expan> a re publica
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente; die restlichen Fragmente sind verschollen, dieser Teil der Inschrift ist jedoch durch einen Abguß überliefert. Z. 6: oder p(ublico?).</p>
            </div>
